Question: Explain to a younger friend how to apply for a college.
Answer:
first, relax.  there is no one right school that you must get in to.  with that in mind, apply to a good number of schools so you have options.  there are great resources online to help get you organized with due dates, so use those and make sure you have all the paperwork ane recommendations necessary.  then, start the applications, which are mostly all the same.  the essay then is the final step - make sure to spend time on it, as it is what separates you from everyone else.